{"tid":2032514,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[有關蘋果一人一信救香港］Facebook 回覆討論","createTime":"2020-05-24T06:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T06:09:27.000Z","uid":286169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cdfb17f0d6290c294c139b1435e28b0dc76c7f","tid":2032514,"uid":286169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"首先post蘋果個連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159047802422448&amp;id=105259197447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10159047802422448%26id%3D105259197447&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=850c2588\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159047802422448&amp;id=105259197447</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxrYgai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxrYgai.png&h=275ff3f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此帖僅想討論facebook步驟，不評論此舉利弊</span>，因為兄弟爬山各自努力，認同嘅自己黎，不認同嘅不作討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦不想在回覆嘥口水</span>。<br />\n<br />\n好，入正題。雖然知道twitter回覆效果好十萬倍，但可能有人只得facebook、但發現回覆步驟不太容易。在此簡單講講我個人嘅處理方法：<br />\n<br />\n1）按蘋果連結，入Donald J. Trump主頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DonaldTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDonaldTrump&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=02f8e1e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DonaldTrump</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 找「Team Trump」的影片，入comment，當中有個來自「Sheila Tam」的回覆<br />\n<br />\n3）按下Sheila Tam回覆下的「回覆」/「Reply」，在他的留言下再以蘋果頭條內容留言<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，目標係推高帖子及某人的留言數，令多些人有機會注意到該回覆，否則根本冇人理。<br />\n<br />\n由於小弟冇乜國際線經驗，做法僅供參考。請高手在留言比多啲改善建議。"},{"pid":"5f368f29aee68edc12792189c7e7ed381a920d0a","tid":2032514,"uid":286169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"【三大方法向特朗普表達訴求】<br />\n<br />\nTwitter：撰寫推文，並上載請願書附圖，標籤 #TrumpSavesHK 和 @realDonaldTrump，或到特朗普Twitter帳戶留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=ca175062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：複製請願書並到特朗普FB專頁留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/DonaldTrump/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FDonaldTrump%2F&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=5488df63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/DonaldTrump/</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：網上簽署白宮聯署（須填寫電郵地址並確認核實）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/one-hongkonger-one-letter-save-hong-kong-trumpsaveshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fone-hongkonger-one-letter-save-hong-kong-trumpsaveshk&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=30705dcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/one-hongkonger-one-letter-save-hong-kong-trumpsaveshk</a>"}]}